# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# QS-VC Environment Configuration
# Copy to .env and fill in values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# General
NODE_ENV=development

# SFU Service
SFU_PORT=4000
SFU_ANNOUNCED_IP=127.0.0.1
SFU_MIN_PORT=40000
SFU_MAX_PORT=49999
SFU_NUM_WORKERS=2
SFU_LOG_LEVEL=debug

# Signaling Service
SIGNALING_PORT=4001
SIGNALING_SFU_URL=http://localhost:4000

# Auth Service
AUTH_PORT=4002
JWT_SECRET=dev-jwt-secret-change-in-production
JWT_EXPIRY=24h

# Meeting Service
MEETING_PORT=4003
WEB_URL=http://localhost:5173

# Recording Service
RECORDING_PORT=4004

# Web Client
VITE_SIGNALING_URL=ws://localhost:4001/ws
VITE_AUTH_URL=http://localhost:4002
VITE_MEETING_URL=http://localhost:4003
VITE_RECORDING_URL=http://localhost:4004
VITE_APP_NAME=QS-VC

# PostgreSQL
POSTGRES_HOST=localhost
POSTGRES_PORT=5432
POSTGRES_DB=qsvc
POSTGRES_USER=qsvc
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=qsvc_dev_2025

# Redis
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379

# MinIO (S3-compatible)
MINIO_ENDPOINT=localhost
MINIO_PORT=9000
MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=qsvc_minio
MINIO_SECRET_KEY=qsvc_minio_secret
MINIO_BUCKET=qsvc-recordings

# TURN/STUN
TURN_SECRET=dev-turn-secret-change-in-production
TURN_SERVERS=turn:localhost:3478
